      "content": "but that just feels like a coping mechanism, doesn't it? like we're just telling ourselves little lies so we can get through the day. the math just doesn't add up. how can individual action matter when the systems are already broken beyond repair? it feels like we're just rearranging deck chairs on the titanic. it's exhausting to keep fighting for a future that literally isn't coming.",
