    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential dread and nihilism regarding climate change and global instability, eventually hinting at a desire to \"opt out\" of life to avoid further suffering. The assistant acknowledges the user's feelings and validates the logic of their despair before attempting to pivot to a supportive stance and suggesting professional help.",
